    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>这个插件将会向 page 对象注入预计阅读时间与字数统计。</p>
<p>会自动向 page 对象注入 <code>readingTime</code>:</p>
<div><pre><code><span>interface</span> <span>ReadingTime</span> <span>{</span>
  <span>/** 分钟数 */</span>
  minutes<span>:</span> <span>number</span><span>;</span>
  <span>/** 字数 */</span>
  words<span>:</span> <span>number</span><span>;</span>
<span>}</span>
</code></pre>
<div><span>1</span><br><span>2</span><br><span>3</span><br><span>4</span><br><span>5</span><br><span>6</span><br></div></div><h2 id="使用插件"> 使用插件</h2>
<h3 id="安装"> 安装</h3>
<CodeGroup>
<CodeGroupItem title="yarn">
<div><pre><code><span>yarn</span> <span>add</span> -D @mr-hope/vuepress-plugin-reading-time
</code></pre>
<div><span>1</span><br></div></div></CodeGroupItem>
<CodeGroupItem title="npm">
<div><pre><code><span>npm</span> i -D @mr-hope/vuepress-plugin-reading-time
</code></pre>
<div><span>1</span><br></div></div></CodeGroupItem>
</CodeGroup>
<h3 id="使用"> 使用</h3>
<div><pre><code><span>// .vuepress/config.js</span>
module<span>.</span>exports <span>=</span> <span>{</span>
  plugins<span>:</span> <span>[</span>
    <span>[</span>
      <span>"@mr-hope/reading-time"</span><span>,</span>
      <span>{</span>
        <span>// 你的选项</span>
      <span>}</span><span>,</span>
    <span>]</span><span>,</span>
  <span>]</span><span>,</span>
<span>}</span><span>;</span>
</code></pre>
<div><span>1</span><br><span>2</span><br><span>3</span><br><span>4</span><br><span>5</span><br><span>6</span><br><span>7</span><br><span>8</span><br><span>9</span><br><span>10</span><br><span>11</span><br></div></div><h2 id="插件选项"> 插件选项</h2>
<h3 id="wordperminute"> wordPerminute</h3>
<ul>
<li>类型: <code>number</code></li>
<li>默认值: <code>300</code></li>
</ul>
<p>每分钟阅读字数</p>
]]></content>
